pullRequest.body:
We remove all `import Mathlib.Mathport.Rename`.

This is done using

```bash
find . -name "*.lean" -exec sed -i '/^import Mathlib.Mathport.Rename/d' {} +
```

plus two fixing by hand of files that were missing various imports.

---
